# Aphasia

Aphasia is a Go project that generates random adjectives and nouns from text files.

## Getting Started

These instructions will get you a copy of the project up and running on your local machine for development and testing purposes.

### Prerequisites

- Go (version 1.16 or later)

### Installing

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/aphasia.git
```

### Usage
- Talk() generates a random mumbled string by combining an adjective and a noun.